summary: AN ORDINANCE Accepting the redevelopment proposal of King Square Associates, LLC to purchase and develop Parcel 49a in the Yesler/Atlantic Neighborhood Improvement Project (Wash. R-5) area; authorizing the Director of the Office of Housing to execute, deliver and administer a contract and deed; designating the disposition of sale proceeds; and ratifying and confirming prior actions.
committee: Housing, Human Services and Civil Rights
